# Frontend Services Layer

Browser API access is centralized in `next-frontend/src/services/`. Prefer these over raw `fetch` in components.

| Service | Use for |
|---------|---------|
| `api.js` | Base axios instance, interceptors, auth header |
| `authService.js` | login, signup, logout, token, `/api/auth/me` |
| `npsApi.js` | Park list, search, park sub-resources |
| `enhancedParkService.js` | Weather, crowd, enhanced park payload |
| `aiService.js` | Plan AI chat, stream, anonymous chat |
| `tripService.js` | TripPlan CRUD, share |
| `tripHistoryService.js` | Local trip list + `migrateLegacyTrips` |
| `conversationService.js` | `/api/conversations` threads |
| `blogService.js` | Blog list, slug, categories |
| `commentService.js` | Blog comments |
| `reviewService.js` | Park reviews |
| `eventService.js` | Events list/register |
| `favoriteService.js` | Saved parks (legacy favorites API) |
| `userService.js` | Profile, saved/visited parks |
| `userPreferencesService.js` | Map state, navigation prefs |
| `dailyFeedService.js` | Park of day, nature facts |
| `testimonialService.js` | Testimonials |
| `discoverApi` is in `lib/discoverApi.js` (not services/) | Discover catalog SSR |
| `analyticsService.js` | Client analytics track |
| `feedbackService.js` | AI feedback |
| `websocketService.js` | Socket.IO realtime |
| `imageUploadService.js` | Image uploads |
| `cacheService.js` / `globalCacheManager.js` | Client caching |
| `batchService.js` / `smartPrefetchService.js` | Performance batching |

## Patterns

- Auth token attached in `api.js` interceptor from cookie/localStorage
- Use `enhancedApi.js` when response needs unified error handling
- Server components should use `getApiBaseUrl()` + `fetch` directly (not these services)

## Legacy

- `src/old_pages/` ‚Äî Vite-era pages; **do not extend**; routes redirect in `next.config.mjs`
